If you really, reallyyy knew me, you‚Äôd know my real purpose in using this platform is not about receiving fire emojis on the pics I post. You‚Äôd know that my main objective is for us all to strive to be our best and live our best life. You‚Äôd know that I‚Äôve absolutely zero shame in using my body to reach more people given it‚Äôs a visual platform, tbh I think I look peachy. You‚Äôd know I‚Äôm confident & comfortable in my own skin & want for us all to be in our own. You‚Äôd know that my quirky captions more often than not have deeeper connotations & you‚Äôd know that I‚Äôm on a mission to inspire ze nation. I just answered one of the 9 questions I am posting here from the podcast I listened to by @jayshetty about eliminating small talk & encouraging more meaningful convos. -
Pick a number, I dare you to answer it in the comments below. NO JUDGMENT ZONE. ‚ù§Ô∏èüëáüëá
1 What was the last lie you told, would you tell it again?
2 If you met your younger self today what would make them happy about you & what would make them sad about you?
3 What type of situation makes you feel awkward and why?
4 What did you buy recently that you now regret?
5 Have you ever been to jail or gotten arrested? 
6 What do you think makes a person most attractive? How attractive are you on that scale? 
7 If you really REALLY knew me, you‚Äôd know that ____________ .
8 What do you fight about most in your romantic relationship?
9 What would you talk about the most in a one hour therapy session? 
#purpose #impact #letstalkmore #mondaymotivation
